      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_109gc' title='Col. 109GC &mdash; HL Deb 21 May 2002 vol 635 c109GC' name='column_109gc' href='#column_109gc' rel='bookmark'>109GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0635P0-02736'>
